>     4\. Faced errors on initializing Trezor hardware wallet emulator

@RohitRanjangit I believe this error indicates you need to create a wallet on the trezor before you can use it (i.e using trezor suite or the online wallet tool). this will prompt you to create a pin and backup your seed phrase. then you will be able to use the wallet with HWI.

apologies, I may have forgotten to mention this step in the testing guide

